---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: help
---
List activity comments

Usage: list [OPTIONS] <ACTIVITY_ID>

Arguments:
  <ACTIVITY_ID>
          Canonical activity ID

Options:
      --limit <N>
          Number of comments to display

          [default: 10]

      --offset <N>
          Zero-based offset into the complete embedded comment collection

          [default: 0]

  -h, --help
          Print help
